permission use url!
	You may create or combine the permissions with role.
	with naming number XX*1000 + YY*10 for example (refresh  execute => 1000 + 10)
	XX:
		0: visit home page and introductions, use tools #implicit 
		1: use refresh
		2: use offline
		3: use diagnostic
		4: use pgp
		5: use ecu control
		6: use user control
		7: use group control
		8: use role control
	YY:
		1000 -> readRefreshLog
		1010 -> signRefreshFile
		
		2000 -> readOfflineLog
		2010 -> readEcuKey
		2020 -> readEcuKeyChange
		2030 -> changeEcuKey
		2040 -> verifyEcuKey
		
		3000 -> readDiagLog 
		3010 -> doDiagExec 

		4000 -> readPgpPublicKey
		4010 -> uploadPgpPublicKey
		4020 -> revokePgpPublicKey
		4030 -> trustPgpPublicKey
		4040 -> untrustPgpPublicKey
		4050 -> deletePgpPublicKey
		
		5000 -> readEcuInfo
		5010 -> createDummyEcu
		5020 -> deleteEcu
		5030 -> readEcuGroup
		5040 -> addEcuIntoGroup
		5050 -> removeEcuFromGroup

		6000 -> #reserved
		
		7000 -> readResourceGroup
		7010 -> createResourceGroup
		7020 -> deleteResourceGroup
		
		8000 -> readRolePermission
		8010 -> readPrivateRole
		8011 -> readGroupRole
		8020 -> grantPrivateRole
		8021 -> grantGroupRole
		8030 -> deletePrivateRole
		8031 -> deleteGroupRole
		

	
		
		
		
	
	
		
		
		
		
	

	